Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(改编自加斯瑞斯克哈尔伯格的小说)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}焰火之城\N第一季第三集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨一直都在这里 没有谁比她更爱音乐了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam was here all the time. No one loves the music like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于小萨来说 音乐就是信仰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For Sam, it's a religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:02:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论有多拥挤 她总能想办法到最前面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't matter how crowded it is, she always finds her way to the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她从不错过任何一场演出 每晚的演出都更精彩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She never missed a show. Every night was better than the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4号那天晚上 有一支乐队在这里表演 他们名叫从无到有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The night of the 4th, a band was playing here, called Ex Nihilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见到萨曼莎了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see Samantha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但是她没留下来看演出 这很不像她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but she didn't stay for the show, which was unlike her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有其他重要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Must've had somewhere real important to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说要去上城 但是会回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Said she was going uptown, but she'd be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我没有再见过她 她还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I didn't see her again. Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨曼莎来的时候是一个人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was Samantha alone when she came by?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一个小伙子一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With a young dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他进去了 不确定他什么时候离开的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He went inside. Not sure when he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿28号的牛仔裤  可能会小便失禁的那种男生吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Size 28 jeans? Type of guy who might piss himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能向人像画师形容他的样子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think you can describe him to a sketch artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定养成了记人脸的习惯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bet you make it a habit to remember faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不习惯告诉警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not talk to cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来警局吧 别人不需要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come by the station. No one has to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 查理 你醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Charlie. You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说有意识了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被你的男友击昏后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After being knocked unconscious by your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 索尔没有用很大力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, Sol didn't hit you that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 我觉得你只是累了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust me. Think you were mostly tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手机和钱包也不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm also missing my cell phone and my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被绑架了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have I been kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 听着 如果扣押我是为索取赎金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, look. If you're holding me for ransom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妈妈可没钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my mom doesn't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是 你看起来并不是“高价值目标”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, no shit. You don't exactly scream "high-value target."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是想问问你昨晚看到了些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We just have some questions about what you saw last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道这不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We know that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...我的意思是 我见到的东西 我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well-- What I meant was, what-- What I did see, I'm--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不明白那是什么 而且我很愿意把它抛到脑后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't understand, and I'm more than willing to forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那你为什么一开始 就在那里鬼鬼祟祟的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No? Why were you creeping around in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把那玩意放下了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you can drop that right fucking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我把它从你的小鸡爪子里 抢过来再插进你屁股之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before I rip it from your bony hands and shove it up your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...但是我不是鬼鬼祟祟 我是来找人帮忙的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-- But I wasn't creeping. I came for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮什么忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What kind of help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨出事了 听说了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you guys hear about Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的小萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个女孩在中央公园被枪击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A girl got shot in Central Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨中枪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam got shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is Sam okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 她还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她处于昏迷状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's in a coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我去过公园 我找到她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I was there in the park, I found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 查理哥们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn, Charlie man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还看到什么了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you see anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有个男的站在她旁边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was this guy standing over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看起来很难过 但...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He seemed upset, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但更像是他发现了她 而不是伤害了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but maybe more like he found her than he hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到警车的声音就跑了 但...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard police sirens and then I ran, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的脑门有个孔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a hole in her forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里到处是血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was blood everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我按时赶到 你知道 要是我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, if I'd been on time, you know, if only I'd--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我却在跳舞 偷喝酒 还嗑嗨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Instead I was dancing, and stealing drinks and getting high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我只是想有好玩的故事 可以讲给她听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I just wanted a good story to tell her, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她爱听有趣的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She loves a good story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道还能去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, I didn't know where else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你们认识小萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, I mean, you guys know Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你们知道为什么 她原计划和我们一起玩 却离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You might know why she made plans to hang out and then just took off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她为什么把我留在夜店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why she left me at that club
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去了一个我们从没 去过的地方 还被枪击了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then went somewhere we'd never gone before and got shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 你们一定要帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, you guys have to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有别的人可问了 我的...妈妈 她只会将我永久禁足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I have no one else. My-- My mom, she'll just ground me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心理医生只会告诉我 说我试图救小萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My therapist will just tell me that I'm trying to save Sam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我当初无法救我爸爸 或别的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I couldn't save my dad, or some--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死在了北塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He died in North Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理哥们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charlie man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来对地方了 我们会查清楚的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You came to the right place. We're gonna figure this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(剧场)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢相信我被你说服了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't believe I let you talk me into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布鲁诺 你爱布鲁诺啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Bruno. You love Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺爱布鲁诺 他是我的艺廊经营者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bruno loves Bruno. He's my gallerist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只在乎一件事 那就是他能卖出去的艺术品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He only cares about one thing and that is art he can sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还带了珍妮来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he brought Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艺廊女生是最糟的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gallery girls are the fucking worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们会讨好你 告诉你你是天才\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How they fawn over you and tell you you're a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真糟糕啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 你好吗  - 嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hi. How are you? - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 这发型啊 - 别说啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This hair, though! - Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己弄的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you do that yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 还是找人弄的呀  - 拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- or did you bring somebody over? - Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 绝对是专业人士 - 专业人士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Professional all the way. - Professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道威廉的问题在哪里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wanna know the problem with William?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你解释 墨瑟 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll explain it to you, Mercer. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 他很清楚我的缺点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please. He's very familiar with my flaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他太有天赋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was too naturally talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...真可悲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's-- How tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 别说了 - 很可怕 真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Stop. - It's awful. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我认真的 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. It's true. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拥有一切 轻而易举 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything has happened for him. Without any effort, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含着金汤匙出生 这辈子从不需要工作一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Born to great wealth. Never needed to work a day in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以当他遇到困难 他视其为失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So when he struggles, he views this as a failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是过程的一部分 懂吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}instead of part of the process. You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 搞心理治疗呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能怪他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的乐队出了一张专辑 那专辑帮助定义了一代人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His band made one album, it helped define a generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他放弃音乐 转向绘画\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then he gives up music to paint,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的首场展览就上了《艺术论坛》的封面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and his first show gets the cover of Art Forum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 从迈阿密到北京 每一位收藏家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, and every collector from Miami to Beijing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在争抢他的作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is fighting over his pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只有一个小问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Except, there's only one little problem--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了 来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here we go. It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们等待 但是再也没有作品了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They wait, but then there's no more art.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来了 作品要来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's coming, the art is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我只需要再多几个月... - 你总是这么对我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I just need a few more months-- - This is what you always say to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也这么和买家说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and so this is what I tell the buyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你知道吗 没有作品 在他们看来 我就成了骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you know what? When there's nothing, they look at me like I'm a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 这 我... - 其实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, I-- - Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常是我和客户打电话联络\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm usually the one on the phone dealing with the clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定有什么可以展示给他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must have something you're ready to show them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他所有时间都花在工作室里 他每天好几个小时都在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He spends all of his time in the studio. He's there every day for hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手头是有创作中的作品 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are some things that I am working on, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想法 其实更像是...概念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are ideas. They're more like-- More of concepts, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:10:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常想看到它们实现潜力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am very excited for them to reach their potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是正如我说的 我需要更多时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, as I've said, I need a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 听着 没有时间了 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Look, there is no more time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 威廉 已经有人开始问 你是不是死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please. William, people are starting to ask me if you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个混蛋 嘿 累积需求越多越好 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What a bastard. Hey! The more pent-up demand is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 这样价格越高 - 拜托 他只是在谦虚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The higher the price is. - Come on. He's just being modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从不认为自己的作品出色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He never thinks anything he does is any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 这交给我们评判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, well, we will be the judge of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是什么意思 你在做什么  - 什么 我们走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What does that mean? What are you doing? - What? We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们去哪里  - 我们去工作室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where are we going? - We're going to the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都得看看你在创作些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all must see what it is that you have been creating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我先喝杯浓缩咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna get an espresso first, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 大家来这里是因为我们都支持你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, everyone is here because we are rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 我们爱你 威廉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right? We love you, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 还需要什么吗  - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Would you like anything else? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 动身 走吧 - 走 去叫辆德士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. Let's go. - Go, get a cab.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们外面见 好吗 我去洗手间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll meet you outside, okay? I'm gonna hit the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:11:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈有夜惊的毛病 会做梦梦见我死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mom has night terrors. Like, dreams where I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她就连让我去上学 都要挣扎一番 你知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it's hard for her to even let me go to school, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她讨厌小萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which means she hated Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小萨将我拉进那个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause Sam pulled me into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉进了她的世界 而那个世界嘛 不太安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Into Sam's world, which is not exactly risk-free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以发生的事可以说是 拉蒙娜威斯巴格最坏的噩梦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what happened was basically Ramona Weisbarger's worst nightmare,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是发生在小萨身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}except it happened to Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也有责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No thanks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真以为自己能够保护她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You really think you could have protected her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 扳倒一个带枪的家伙  - 不...我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Taken down a guy with a gun? - No. I--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我在场 我愿意为她挡下子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I would have taken a bullet for her if I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解释了你为什么带着这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Explains why you've been carrying this around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(钦定版圣经)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先知查理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charlie, the Prophet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我读都没读过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I haven't even read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不确定如果读了我是否会相信 但...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure if I'd even believe it if I did. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜里面有关于宽恕的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}presumably, there's something about forgiveness in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在需要那个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what you need right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常需要 我甚至无法呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So bad I can hardly breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理 好的 闭上眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Charlie. Okay, close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着萨曼莎 让她充满你的思绪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think of Samantha. Let the thought of her fill you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在睁开眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我 直直看着我 别移开目光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at me. Right at me. Don't look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《圣经》说所有真正忏悔的罪孽者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Bible says that all sinners who truly repent,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应被施以极大的慈悲 被宽恕所有的罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}shall be granted great mercy and forgiven all offenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论我们做了什么或为什么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't matter what we've done, or why we did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是上帝的律法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the law of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我不是牧师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I'm no priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是一个有在主日学校好好听课的小孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a kid who paid attention in Sunday school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里就我们两个男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I am the only other guy here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味着赦罪的职责只能落在我肩上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which means the job of absolution falls on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理威斯巴格 我赦免你的罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charlie Weisbarger, I absolve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已被赦免\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are absolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 小子 发生在小萨身上的事 并不是你的错 听到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, kid, what happened to Sam is not your fault. You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 发生在小萨身上的事不是我的错 - 不 要真的相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What happened to Sam was not my fault. - Nah, a little more like you mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生在小萨身上的事不是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to Sam was not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来 喊出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You stand up and yell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 发生在小萨身上的事不是我的错 - 喊出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What happened to Sam was not my fault. - Yell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 发生在小萨身上的事不是我的错 - 大声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What happened to Sam was not my fault. - Louder!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生在小萨身上的事不是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to Sam was not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然 它还处在理论阶段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Obviously, it's living in a theoretical space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(点)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它变得更具体有形的生命之旅刚开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just beginning its life journey into a more tangible form.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这是个停车标志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that's a stop sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经是停车标志 现在是“点”标志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, it was a stop sign, but now it is a "spot" sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 哟 就...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Yo, just--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象一下 在纽约街头遇到这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Imagine encountering this in the streets of New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 因为街道是唯一一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, because the streets is the only place
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们会见到这种垃圾的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where anyone is going to see this piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉 你还有别的作品吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have anything else, William?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有已经完成到这一步的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, nothing that is as far along as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比“点”标志更完整的作品  我不懂了 威廉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Far along as a "spot" sign? I don't understand, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是泡在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After all the time you've been spending here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你唯一能交出来的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this is all you have to show for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 墨瑟 别说了 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please. Mercer, please. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他显然只是来这里吸毒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is obvious he has been coming here only to get high.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你现在已经嗑嗨了 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not to mention that you are high right now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 你瞧 你浪费了我的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. See? You have wasted my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是更糟的是你浪费了自己的才华\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But worse, you are wasting your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有争议 但我挺喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Controversial, but I kind of love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你在剧场餐厅的洗手间注射毒品了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you shot up in the bathroom at Odeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没办法在桌子上弄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not like I could've just done it right there at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克纳利对那种行为不待见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}McNally sort of frowns at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你说过要戒的 - 我会戒的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You said you were quitting. - I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在戒 好吗 宝贝 我真的想戒 我会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am, okay? Babe. I really want to. I'm going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的是不再为了这件事争吵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I want is to stop having this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这样要怎么走下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are we supposed to go on like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们不该走下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we're not supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在走一条黑暗的道路 威廉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're going down a dark road, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽头是一个“点”标志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One that ends in a "spot" sign
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外什么都没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾根 我们不知道你会来 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Regan, we weren't expecting you, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝鸡蛋 口感像云一样很松软\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try the eggs. It's like eating a cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不会留下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I'm not staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里只是因为我觉得让爸爸和我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just here because I thought it might be nice for Daddy and I
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走进办公室比较好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to walk into the office together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对他来说会是艰难的一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's gonna be a rough day for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有人把审前传讯泄露给媒体了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}since someone leaked the pretrial arraignment to the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(汉密尔顿斯维尼集团老板 因欺诈指控被起诉)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了 真是卑鄙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw. Nasty stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为我们人缘很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I thought people liked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们喜欢丑闻 无论谁受损\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People like scandal at anyone's expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 爸爸 你没穿好衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi, Daddy. You're not dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莫里和菲莉希亚没告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Amory and Felicia didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天不去上班 或者说 以后也不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not going in today. Or ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人告诉过我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the first I'm hearing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的错 这是他审前释放的条件之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My failing. It's a condition of his pretrial release.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我读过协议 上面根本没提到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I read the agreement and it said nothing about him
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不去办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not going into the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在附件备忘录里写的 以防协议被泄露\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was in a side memo in case the agreement was leaked,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也的确被泄露了 那帮秃鹰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as it was, the fucking vultures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当是退休吧 我已经开始策划派对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll call it retirement. I've already started planning the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一比你父亲的辩护更重要的是他的健康\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only thing more important than your father's defense is his health.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样他可以同时关注于两件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This way, he can focus on both.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律师可以来这里办事 一切都是私下处理 舒舒服服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The lawyers can come here to work. Everything very private, comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 这是你想要的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dad, is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 这是大家想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darling, it's what everyone wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你努力工作 创造美好的人生 然后终于能享受了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You work hard to create a beautiful life, then you finally get to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说 越早享受越好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The sooner the better, I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 你去 照常工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You go, sweetie. Business as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,董事会得看到你可以处理好事务 在没有我的情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The board needs to see that you can handle things. Without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会打电话给你的 我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'll call you. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不给我她的号码 请直接打给她 这事很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you won't give me her number, please just call her, it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 再说一次 我叫墨... - 墨瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Once again my name is M-- - Mercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 兰普莱特太太 我不知道你认识他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, Mrs. Lamplighter. I didn't realize that you knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, really? And why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我可投票给了丁肯斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. I voted for Dinkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来看我父亲 你为什么来这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was just stopping by to see my father. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道在这个地方能找到你 这事不能等 是关于威廉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was the only place I knew to find you. It couldn't wait. It's William.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今晚会在我们的公寓组织戒毒干预会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're having an intervention at our apartment tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他会很不喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. He's gonna hate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他更不喜欢的是死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not as much as he'll hate being dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经那么严重了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他想要帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know he wants help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使他不开口要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if he won't ask for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我承担下责任 去找任何还在乎威廉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I've just been tasked with finding any of William's friends and family
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友和家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who still care about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是 - 希望这包括你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. - I hope that includes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(前事追溯 《黄铜战术》)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨是一位艺术家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam is an artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这里用作她的工作室 也可能是储藏间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Used this place as her studio, or maybe a storage locker,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不知道这有什么重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but not sure how any of this matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的直觉是小萨认识开枪的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My instinct is Sam knew her shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉这不是意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This doesn't feel like a "wrong place, wrong time" situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨曼莎没有被袭击 没有物品被偷走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Samantha wasn't assaulted. Nothing was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一枪打偏了 第二枪击中了她 但是没有要她的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First shot went wide, second one got her, but didn't kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个枪击者没有留下来确认这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fact that the shooter didn't stick around to verify, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}very thankful for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这让我觉得 这是私人恩怨 但是业余人士做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it makes me think that this was personal, but amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有动机的枪手 但没什么经验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A shooter with a motive, but not a lot of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本案的大部分物证都用不上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}most of the physical evidence in this case is shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们找到这凶手的途径就是动机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, the way we find this perp is motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说要尽可能了解关于你女儿的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That means learning everything we can about your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有孩子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got any kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有 正在努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not yet. I'm working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你完全不懂我的心情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you've no goddamn clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一出生起 你就尽一切努力去保护他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Moment they're born, you do everything you can to protect them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后却发生了这样的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then something like this happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杨先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, Mr. Yeung.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你经历过最艰难的一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the hardest thing you're ever gonna go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都需要依靠些什么来支撑自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And everybody needs something to lean on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来维持信念 对我来说 我相信的是一位父亲的爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To believe in. For me, I believe in a father's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要找到对她做了这事的人 但没有你的帮助就做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're gonna find who did this to her, but not without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有谁比你更了解萨曼莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know Samantha better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她最喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That one's her favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说音乐对于昏迷中的人来说有益\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I think I heard that music is good for people in comas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们与现实保持联结\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keeps them connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到手机了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You find a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 她有手机吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Did she have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没给我她的号码 但我见她用过几次手机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never gave me her number, but I saw her on it a couple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 也许是某个 不希望我们知道她和谁交朋友的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could be someone who didn't want us to know who her friends were.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会想看看这个的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll wanna see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫这个杂志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She calls it a zine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在弄这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was always working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是去金考店打印\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heading over to Kinko's all hours, making copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想了解我的女儿 那信息都在这里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you wanna know my daughter, it's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你为什么会在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, how'd you end up down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.14,0:22:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是因为我喜欢过山车吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess because I love roller coasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈在我16岁时去世\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mom died when I was 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有爸爸 所以在那之后 我就从路易斯安那一路北上流浪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No dad, so I just kind of drifted up north from Louisiana after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从孟菲斯 到纳什维尔 辛辛那提 清理旅店房间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cleaned motel rooms from Memphis to Nashville to Cincinnati.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.82,0:22:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我听说俄亥俄桑达斯基的杉点游乐园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I heard about Cedar Point in Sandusky, Ohio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一个有18个世界级过山车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Figured a place with 18 world-class roller coasters
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一个水上乐园的地方应该不会太糟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a water park couldn't be all bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:22:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你对清理旅店房间 有什么了解 查理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what you've heard about cleaning motel rooms, Charlie,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这是个低工资 高风险的职业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's a low-pay, high-risk profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在短时间内赚到钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Math only goes your way for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就不赚钱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then it goes the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.10,0:23:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他们叫你“下水道女孩”的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's why they call you Sewer Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你住在下水道或...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause you were, like, living in the gutters or--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.86,0:23:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 尼基说我困在 某种较低水平的意识层面上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Nicky says I'm stuck on a lower level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仍然会因为可爱的动物照片而感动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I still get sentimental about cute animal pics
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我的星座这类玩意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and my horoscope and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.45,0:23:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说等我成长后我可以选个新的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He says I can pick a new name once I evolve,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.37,0:23:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我好像习惯这名字了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I don't know, kinda used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.34,0:23:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 抱歉 那么 尼基是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, sorry, wha-- So, what's the deal with Nicky?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.25,0:23:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为他是翻唱乐队的主唱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought he was, like, the lead singer in a cover band?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.22,0:23:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂 查理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't get it, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你会懂的 乐队只是个幌子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you will. The band is the cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.31,0:24:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.32,0:24:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.37,0:24:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.80,0:24:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 这是乐队的排练地点 但我们正在翻改\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. This is the band's rehearsal space, but we're converting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.05,0:24:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要知道改成什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To what, you don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.39,0:24:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这些设备都要搬到地下室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But all this equipment goes into the basement,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.26,0:24:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗户得封上 地毯得移除\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the window needs to be covered and the carpet has to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.56,0:24:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多地毯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a lot of carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.44,0:24:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你最好马上开始干活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you better get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.94,0:24:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我要一个人做吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, I'm doing this all by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.82,0:24:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是尼基的主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was this Nicky's idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.07,0:24:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里发生的一切都是尼基的主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing happens here that isn't Nicky's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.18,0:26:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 是给我的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. Is that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.14,0:26:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么和你一点也无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's none of your goddamn business is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.78,0:27:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(证据)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.45,0:27:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(乌托邦 破裂的混沌)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.45,0:27:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(假装不孤独)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.62,0:27:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很笨拙 像只小狗 眼神无辜 面带微笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was awkward. Like a puppy. Sweet-eyed. Smiley.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.63,0:27:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许有些雀斑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe some freckles.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.09,0:27:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的头发是卷的 白人男孩的卷发 拖把发型\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And his hair was curly. White boy curly. A mop.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.64,0:27:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.26,0:27:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.39,0:27:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真准啊 那孩子就是只小奶狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nailed it. That kid's a fucking labradoodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.89,0:27:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 枪击 什么枪击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait. A shooting? What shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.98,0:27:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在派对外面 中央公园的女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The-- Right outside the party. The girl in Central Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.94,0:27:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的孩子是纽约大学的学生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poor thing was an NYU student.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.20,0:27:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨瑟发现了她 把外套盖在她身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mercer found her and put his jacket over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.82,0:27:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...威廉的外套 因为是他借的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's like-- It was William's jacket, 'cause he borrowed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.74,0:27:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 当警察找到毒品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then when the cops found the drugs,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.37,0:27:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨瑟意识到威廉是个瘾君子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's when Mercer realized that William's a fucking junkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.71,0:27:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩 她还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is she okay, this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.09,0:27:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还知道关于她的其他信息吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know anything else about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.09,0:27:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她处于昏迷状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, she's in a coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.68,0:28:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会公布其他信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they're not releasing any other information.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.01,0:28:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说她是大一生 我不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apparently she's a freshman, I think. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.93,0:28:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是大一生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's freshman.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.02,0:28:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么区别呢 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What difference does it make, really, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.85,0:28:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对 是啊 就是个悲剧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're right. Yeah, it's tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.77,0:28:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 我好紧张 我太紧张了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God. I'm so nervous. I am so fucking nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.32,0:28:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.78,0:28:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.03,0:28:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Regan,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.11,0:28:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要召开紧急董事会会议 我们得在办公室开会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's an emergency board meeting. We need to convene at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.03,0:28:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 今晚吗  - 恐怕如此 时间紧迫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Tonight? - Afraid so. It's time-sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.29,0:28:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能去 重新安排时间吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't. Just reschedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.58,0:28:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让吉斯看孩子没问题吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, surely Keith can watch the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.17,0:28:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我们担心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As we feared,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.29,0:28:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,董事会非常担忧比尔面临的指控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the board is extremely concerned about the charges against Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.00,0:28:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就向他们保证他是无辜的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So then reassure them that he's innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.92,0:28:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你能不能... - 我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can you get--? - Well, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.05,0:28:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我显然一再保证了 但... - 孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Obviously, I have, strenuously, but-- - Kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.47,0:28:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莫里 是威廉的事 他遇到麻烦了 我得去帮他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Amory, it's William. He's in trouble, and I need to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.64,0:28:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉 我不知道你们有联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}William. I hadn't realized you'd connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.69,0:28:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉让你为难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry to put you in this position
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.48,0:28:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼你在父亲和弟弟之间做选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}having to choose between your father and your brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.44,0:28:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是目前的现实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but this is where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.32,0:28:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你需要 随时找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.03,0:29:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 艾莫里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodbye, Amory.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.08,0:29:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我想说 我会的 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I wanted to share, I would. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.29,0:29:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 你的最爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My dear, your favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.00,0:29:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 三文鱼 - 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Salmon. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.63,0:29:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 我不能迟到 我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God. I cannot be late. I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.46,0:29:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你会留下 妈妈 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're staying. Right, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.42,0:29:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 宝贝 对不起 我不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Sweetie, I'm sorry. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.97,0:29:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来给你们做晚餐的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just came to make you dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.51,0:29:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该感谢妈妈做晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which we should thank her for.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.51,0:29:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了 凯特 放弃吧 他们不会复合的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you, Cate. Give it up. They're not getting back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.10,0:29:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿 我们又不知道 - 我们知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, we don't know that. - Yeah, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.40,0:29:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 没什么比家庭更重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still, there's nothing more important than family.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.61,0:29:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.24,0:29:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.95,0:29:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔 尝尝吧 拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will, just try it, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.93,0:30:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天看够了 欣赏得开心吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got an eyeful today. Like what you saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.22,0:30:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说不喜欢 我只是不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't not like it. I just don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.60,0:30:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是索尔的女友 对吧  所以你也和尼基在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're Sol's girl, right? So, are you with Nicky too, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.73,0:30:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有你那种乡巴佬式的玻璃心 我不会为此道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't apologize for not conforming to your delicate suburban sensibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.78,0:30:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夫一妻只是父权制度资本主义的工具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monogamy is just a tool of patriarchal capitalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.66,0:30:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来像是小萨会说的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That sounds exactly like something that Sam would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.33,0:30:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我则会假装理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that I would, like, pretend to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.49,0:30:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨是个笃信者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam is a believer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.20,0:30:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笃信什么 随便和人上床\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A believer in what, sleeping around?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.54,0:30:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说 小萨在守身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you ask me, Sammy's saving herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.92,0:30:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为谁守身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.84,0:30:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道 也许是你呢 查理哥们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who knows? Could be you, Charlie man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.93,0:30:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.26,0:30:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始这场革命时 就知道会有代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we started this revolution, we knew it would have a cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.98,0:31:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚 我们要致敬 一位正在为自己的生命而战的受伤战士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And tonight, we celebrate a wounded warrior fighting for her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.61,0:31:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬小萨 今晚是献给她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To Sam. Tonight's for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.11,0:31:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 敬小萨 - 小萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- To Sammy. - To Sam. - To Sammy. - Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.07,0:31:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫为了小萨 我们在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's for Sam? What are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.79,0:31:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都不认识这小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't even know this fucking kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.92,0:31:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以非常快的速度进入了我们的圈子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He has had a rather rapid ascent into our good graces,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.00,0:31:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他给我们带来什么好处了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but what does he bring to the table, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.84,0:31:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨喜欢他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam likes him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.92,0:31:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 她什么都没和他说 那我们为什么要说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah? Well, she didn't tell him shit. So, why should we?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.30,0:31:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 无论小萨知道什么 我也想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, well, whatever Sam knew, I wanna know too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.39,0:31:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我打晕 将我锁起来 逼我做苦工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Knock me out. Lock me up. Force me into hard labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.06,0:31:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便什么 我什么都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever. I'm all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.69,0:31:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.82,0:31:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他什么都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.07,0:31:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走着瞧吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guess we'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.12,0:31:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零点即将到来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The zero hour is upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.66,0:31:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们玩点好玩的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.05,0:32:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 别紧张 威廉不会敲门的 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Relax. William wouldn't knock. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.73,0:32:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 - 嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hi. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.35,0:32:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 真感谢你来 - 是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you so much for coming. - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.77,0:32:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾根 这是维纳斯德尼龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Regan, this is Venus De Nylon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.94,0:32:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 我是威廉的姐姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi. I'm William's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.40,0:32:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他有个姐姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't know he had a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.78,0:32:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维纳斯曾是前事追溯的键盘手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Venus played keyboard for Ex Post Facto.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.78,0:32:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须由我代表乐队来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Had to represent.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.87,0:32:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原乐队的人要不就是比比利的情况更严重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone from the original band's either more fucked up than Billy,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.29,0:32:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不就是恨他或是已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hates him or is already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.25,0:32:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还在世的人只能尽我们所能了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we who are living will have to do everything that we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.09,0:32:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.26,0:32:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.68,0:32:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 请坐 - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Have a seat. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.76,0:32:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.89,0:32:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想说声谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just wanted to say thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.10,0:33:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你在威廉身边没人的时候 陪伴和支持他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for being there for William when no one else was.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.31,0:33:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.90,0:33:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.98,0:33:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是 - 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.03,0:33:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉随时可能走进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any moment now, William's gonna walk through that door,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.15,0:33:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他大概不会喜欢眼前的景象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he is probably not gonna like what he sees.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.91,0:33:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们是来这里告诉他你们爱他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you're here to tell him that you love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.91,0:33:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱意味着要承担责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Love makes people accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.13,0:33:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(中央公园枪击案尚无嫌犯)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.81,0:33:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 我是小萨 请留言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, you've reached Sam. Please leave a message,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.06,0:33:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以用怀旧的方式 打我的传呼机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or you can do it the old-fashioned way and page me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.81,0:33:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,语音信箱已满 无法接收任何讯息...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mailbox is full and cannot accept any messages--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.25,0:34:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(西西亚罗意大利餐厅)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.51,0:35:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好 - 嗨 桑托斯太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hello. - Hey, Mrs. Santos.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.76,0:35:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我的电话不算太迟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope I haven't called too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.08,0:35:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 威廉 我叫厄尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, William. My name's Earl.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.63,0:35:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天这些善良的人们聚在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These good folks here gathered today
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.13,0:35:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为他们担心你会死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because they're afraid that you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.97,0:35:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想坐下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you like to have a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.35,0:35:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 厄尔 我不坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Earl, I would not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.19,0:35:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 威廉 听我说 这是我的主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, listen. This was my idea, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.07,0:35:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以生我的气 但是最重要的是 你需要生自己的气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you can be mad at me, but mostly, you need to be mad at yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.53,0:36:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的毒瘾正在削弱 你作为艺术家的作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because your addiction is diminishing your work as an artist,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.70,0:36:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你的谎言则在削弱你的人格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but your lying, your lying is diminishing you as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.87,0:36:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以求求你 不要表现得 像是你不需要这次干预\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So please, please don't act like you are better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.58,0:36:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说完了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're done?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.38,0:36:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厄尔只是在尽本职 我很感谢他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Earl here is just doing his job. And I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.85,0:36:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是布鲁诺 我也理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck. I mean, Bruno, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.77,0:36:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有作品给你售卖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have nothing for you to sell,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.69,0:36:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我对你来说没有价值\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and therefore I am of no value to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.41,0:36:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你 宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.33,0:36:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.17,0:36:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真觉得这会有用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you really think this was gonna work?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.38,0:36:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不认为这会有用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He didn't think this would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.05,0:36:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是没别的办法向你表达他爱你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's just running out of ways to show you that he loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.80,0:37:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪位啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.84,0:37:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请...别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't-- Please don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.43,0:37:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可真佩服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.85,0:37:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 小蕾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Reegs.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.65,0:37:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多久了 15年了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What-- What has it been, 15 years, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.90,0:37:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 差不多吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Give or take.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.45,0:37:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.82,0:37:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用了那么久时间找到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's how long it took me to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.95,0:37:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.08,0:37:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 别离开 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't do that. Don't go. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.08,0:37:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.42,0:37:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我的天啊 - 不 我非常想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, my God. - No, I miss you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.84,0:37:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我现在不能做这件事 我做不到 - 我从没停止想念你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I can't do this right now. I can't. - I never stopped missing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.22,0:37:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到我并没那么难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't that hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.10,0:37:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 所以无论这是在做什么... - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So whatever this is... - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.27,0:37:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我之前有个乐队 我们出了一张专辑 - 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I was in a band. We made an album. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.56,0:37:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在一家画廊开了展览\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had a show at a gallery that was reviewed
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.11,0:38:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《纽约时报》都登了评论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by The New York fucking Times.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.11,0:38:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我距离你从来都不超过20分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was never more than 20 minutes away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.53,0:38:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走路就能找到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You could have walked.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.54,0:38:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个家庭 我有两个孩子 我之前结婚了 有工作 我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had a family. I had two kids. I was married. I had a job. I was--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.62,0:38:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在原地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was right fucking there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.12,0:38:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 就在你离开我的地方 没有动过 - 在...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Right where you left me. Right there. - Where--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.05,0:38:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我离开你的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where I left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.76,0:38:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你和我一起离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.77,0:38:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乞求你和我一起离开 我只是想要保护你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I fucking begged you to come with me. I just wanted to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.82,0:38:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我们的父亲保护你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted our father to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.40,0:38:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道还能做什么 我如履薄冰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't know what else to do. I was hanging on by a fucking thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.36,0:38:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须想办法生存下去 我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had to find a way to survive. I didn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.16,0:38:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 恭喜你啊 小蕾 - 拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, congratulations, Reegs... - Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.33,0:38:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你活下来了 你熬出头了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...that you survived. You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.37,0:38:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.33,0:39:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不用做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.38,0:39:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.09,0:39:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不认识这些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't even know these people,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.80,0:39:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我希望你明白我有多爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I wish you understood how much I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.97,0:39:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道爸爸病了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know that Dad is sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.06,0:39:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.98,0:39:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他会张开双臂迎接你回家吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know that he would welcome you back with open fucking arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.23,0:39:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸是个懦夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daddy is a fucking coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.98,0:39:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个懦夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.11,0:39:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所有人都是懦夫 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of you, everyone here is a fucking coward! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.28,0:39:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 注射毒品就是你所谓的勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, and shooting dope is your idea of bravery?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.87,0:39:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最酷了 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're so fucking cool, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.58,0:39:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来我们有许多要讨论的 大家都坐下 先喝点茶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounds like there is a lot to discuss. So let's all sit and just have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.09,0:39:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧 这就是为什么我回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see, this is why I came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.38,0:39:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是这里是我家 所以 感谢你们大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remembered it was here. So, thank you all very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.59,0:39:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉 你现在可以改变 整个人生 只需要一个决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}William, you can change your whole life right now with just one decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.39,0:40:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 威廉 听听他的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, William, will you just listen to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.40,0:40:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 求求你 你以后会谢我... - 闭嘴 拜托闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm begging you. You'll thank me-- - Shut up! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.90,0:40:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 墨瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop. Mercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.37,0:40:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有我跟着厄尔离开这里 你才肯爱我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, if I leave with Earl here, it's the only way you'll love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.04,0:40:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想要那样的爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want that kind of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.38,0:40:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 谢了 我不要那个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, thank you. I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.19,0:40:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.04,0:41:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 托尼 你好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Tony. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.54,0:41:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的 我今晚会和家人一起去阿斯彭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, I'm heading to Aspen with the family tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.17,0:41:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以顺路把文件给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could drop the paperwork on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.42,0:41:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 谢谢 方便吗 我带着文件呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, thank you. Is that gonna work? I got it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.55,0:41:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 行 太好了 好 一会儿见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. All right, great. All right, I'll see you in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.83,0:41:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.20,0:41:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你想要回这文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm guessing you want this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.54,0:41:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫小萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.30,0:41:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 小萨 - 嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, Sam. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.68,0:42:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(兰兹曼宿舍)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.23,0:42:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(纽约大学)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.11,0:42:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(仅限住户 进入需出示身份证件)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.47,0:42:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉太不妥了 我们换个地方吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is so wrong. Let's go anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.80,0:42:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不 - 联合广场有家W酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. - There's a W in Union Square.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.47,0:42:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样有趣多了 11点之后男生禁入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is way more fun. There are no boys allowed after 11:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.18,0:42:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 男生  - 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Boys? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.89,0:42:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.92,0:43:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(保护它们的家园 爱熊猫)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.17,0:43:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.63,0:43:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你室友的熊猫癖让整件事更奇怪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your roommate's panda fetish isn't making this any less weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.68,0:43:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去得梅因度假了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's in Des Moines for the holidays,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.80,0:43:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 所以把焦点放在我身上 别想她 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- so you can focus on me, not her. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.72,0:43:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢 你有什么癖好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about you? What are you into?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.18,0:43:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为看起来你都没在这里住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause it looks like you don't even live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.23,0:43:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的癖好是你 你知道我住在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm into you. And you know where I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.24,0:43:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Speaking of...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.62,0:43:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.70,0:43:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解你后 我意识到我其实...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now that I know you, I realized I don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.66,0:43:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实并不真的了解你 一个已婚的金融男\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't really know you. A married finance guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.67,0:43:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会闯入我的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you end up on my doorstep?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.39,0:44:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有秘密的不只是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not the only one with secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.14,0:44:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我没有秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who, me? I'm an open book.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.19,0:44:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你说过最大的谎了 瞧瞧你说得多么自然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the biggest lie you've told yet. Look how easily it came.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.86,0:44:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 告诉我你为谁工作 - 没有谁 我是自雇人士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Tell me who you work for. - No one. I'm self-employed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.12,0:44:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都有顶头上司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone answers to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.89,0:44:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.35,0:44:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's my door.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.35,0:44:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.27,0:44:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自得梅因的熊猫爱好者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Panda lover from Des Moines.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.69,0:44:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是萨曼莎的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a friend of Samantha's.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.99,0:45:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是好奇 不知道你是否知道她最近如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was just wondering if you knew how she's doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.70,0:45:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是最近几天有没有见过她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or if you've seen her in the last couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.45,0:45:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 警察也在好奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, the cops wondered that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.12,0:45:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察来过这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The cops were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.62,0:45:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I--
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.63,0:45:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 能不能问你...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, can I ask you--
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.67,0:45:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨说今年秋季她会升大四\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam told me she was gonna be a senior this fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.38,0:45:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她是去年秋季入学的 她是大一生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. She started last fall. She's a freshman.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.37,0:45:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(纽约市警察局 阿里帕尔撒)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.47,0:46:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我明天午饭可以 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. I can do lunch tomorrow. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.80,0:46:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂姆 我很感谢你总是支持我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tim, I appreciate that you've always had my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.51,0:46:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 我们保持联系 好的 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. We'll stay in touch. All right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.56,0:46:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾根 和威廉的重聚怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Regan, how did the reunion go with William?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.31,0:46:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常短暂 另外 我显然来迟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was short-lived. And I see I'm too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.19,0:46:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不会 艾莫里赶来 挽救了局面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not at all. Amory has swooped in and saved the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.28,0:46:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们找到合适人选接任你父亲之前 他会担任临时主席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's interim chair until we can find a suitable replacement for your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.20,0:46:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,董事会很满意 船趋向稳定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The board is very happy. The ship has been steadied.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.41,0:46:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 或是被劫持了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, or hijacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.33,0:46:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逼迫我父亲退休\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, you force my father into retirement
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.17,0:46:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后首席执行官的职位 就自然而然落到你头上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then the CEO job just falls right into your lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.26,0:46:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临时的 在我们找到永久替任人选之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Interim. Until we can find a permanent replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.09,0:46:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉你弟弟那边的事不顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry things didn't go so well with your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.76,0:46:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也需要你 此刻比以往更需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I need you too, now more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.52,0:46:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.06,0:46:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早上见吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.69,0:46:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.57,0:47:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都别说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.51,0:47:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊 先知 你在正中央\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Prophet. Front and center.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.01,0:47:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 过来 嘿 - 什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come here. Hey. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.80,0:47:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“Ne cede malis” 意思是 “勿向邪恶屈首”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ne cede malis. Means "yield not to evil."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.19,0:47:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是布朗克斯的座右铭 来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the motto of the Bronx. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.74,0:47:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fucking beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.04,0:47:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理哥们 怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the matter, Charlie man?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.25,0:48:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂我们在这做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand what we're doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.88,0:48:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨热爱音乐 她不喜欢暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam loves music. She's not into violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.93,0:48:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 她不会伤害任何人 - 我们也不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She'd never hurt anybody. - And neither would we.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.26,0:48:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 查理 那栋楼里没人住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay, Charlie. No one lives in that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.81,0:48:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.56,0:48:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨也问过同样的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam asked the same questions you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.56,0:48:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尽力回答了 我们爱这座城市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tried my best to answer. We love this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.61,0:48:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为它应该属于音乐人和艺术创造者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We think it should belong to the musicians and the artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.45,0:48:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于黑人和棕色人种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To the Black and the brown folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.12,0:48:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于梦想者 瘾君子和诗人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To the dreamers, the junkies, the poets.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.96,0:48:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一些很坏的人 正试图将城市从我们手中夺走 而...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But some very bad people are trying to take that away from us, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.80,0:48:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是在反击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we're just fighting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.88,0:48:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过放火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By setting it on fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.09,0:48:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你必须相信我 先知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, you're gonna have to trust me, Prophet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.39,0:48:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.68,0:48:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为民众守住这座城市的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A plan to keep this city for the people
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.89,0:49:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将那些偷走我们岛屿的混蛋们关进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and lock up those bastards who are stealing our island.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.64,0:49:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在建造一个新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're building a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.65,0:49:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那需要先摧毁旧世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that requires the destruction of the old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.52,0:49:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且烧毁东西的感觉妙极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Also, it feels really fucking good to blow shit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.28,0:49:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 太美妙了 - 可不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So fucking good. - Hell yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.99,0:49:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们唱和这有关的歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We sang songs about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.50,0:49:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你问的是“小萨会怎么做 ”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the question you're asking is, "What would Sam do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.96,0:49:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得大家都知道答案 小萨曾是我们的一份子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think we all know the answer. Sam was one of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.59,0:49:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你反其道而行 你是无法接近真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you're not gonna get closer to the truth of what happened to her
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.09,0:49:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查出她发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}running in the other direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.30,0:49:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 查理 加入我们 让小萨看见你的本领\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Charlie. Join us. Show Sam what you're made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.73,0:49:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...国庆日中央公园枪击案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...a person of interest in the July 4th shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.23,0:49:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现一名嫌疑人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in Central Park has been identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.32,0:49:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(纽约警局公布公园枪击案嫌疑人照片)\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Police are looking for a Caucasian male between 15 and 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.07,0:49:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方在寻找一个15至25岁的白人男性
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.32,0:49:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中等身高 身材苗条 深色头发和眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Medium height, slim build, dark hair and eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.49,0:49:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如任何人有任何信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyone with information,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.83,0:50:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拨打212-111-TIPS联络纽约警局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}please call the NYPD at 212-111-TIPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.63,0:50:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公园枪击...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As shootings in the park--
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.42,0:50:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苗条的小孩 浓密的头发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Skinny kid, bushy hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.17,0:50:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像头上趴了只贵宾狗尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like a poodle died on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.55,0:50:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是个小孩 他是个40岁的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wasn't a kid. He was, like, 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.01,0:50:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵族学院风 打扮干净利落 戴着劳力士表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Preppy, clean-cut, Rolex.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.07,0:50:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把录像带调出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go pull that tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.90,0:50:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是28号牛仔裤的小孩 那是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it's not the 28 jeans kid, then who the hell is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.99,0:50:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.91,0:50:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是 - 嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.20,0:50:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片里的小孩 他母亲打来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The kid in the photo, his mother called in.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.37,0:50:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 是的 我这就过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, yeah. I'll head right over.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.21,0:50:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南汉普顿的夏天 许多美好的回忆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Summers in Southampton. So many good memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.93,0:51:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事还是忘记为好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some things are better left forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.73,0:51:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 来吧 查理 - 来吧 先知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on, Charlie. - Come on, Prophet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.44,0:51:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你能做到 查理 呼吸 - 来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You can do it, Charlie. Breathe. - Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.07,0:51:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们相信你 - 加油\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We believe in you. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.41,0:51:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 别多想 - 来吧 先知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Don't even think about it. - Come on, Prophet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.99,0:51:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔就是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just throw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.86,0:51:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们可以走了 - 走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We can head out. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.03,0:51:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.11,0:51:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 查理哥们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Charlie man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.82,0:51:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啊 查理 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Charlie man! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.13,0:52:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(警方戒严线 请勿跨越)
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.98,0:52:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keith?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.65,0:52:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事这么急 不能等到明早再说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what was so urgent that it couldn't wait till morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.86,0:52:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是女孩中枪的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is where the girl was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.74,0:52:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我从派对上看到警察了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I saw the police from the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.66,0:52:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对这个案件有特别的兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a special interest in this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.63,0:52:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在想...我是说...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was just won-- I mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.75,0:52:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我知道她是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I know who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.92,0:53:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想不知你是否知道...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I was wondering if you knew if...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.81,0:53:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you--
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.06,0:53:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否知道...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you knew about--
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.06,0:53:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯 一个年轻女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keith, what is there to know about a young girl
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.61,0:53:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一个已婚男人之间有什么隐情  而且后者的好福气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a married man who owes his good fortune,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.03,0:53:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更别提他实际的财富 都来自他挚爱妻子的家族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not to mention his actual fortune, to his lovely wife's family?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.07,0:53:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一个男人肯定不会 将公私生活混在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Surely such a man wouldn't mix business with that kind of pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.41,0:53:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那不明智\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. That wouldn't be smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.37,0:53:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是十足的愚蠢 甚至是危险的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would be pure stupidity. It would be dangerous even.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.17,0:53:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 艾莫里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus, Amory.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.47,0:53:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里发生的事是因为你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened here, is it because of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.18,0:53:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 吉斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Keith.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.97,0:53:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都知道这里发生的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We both know that what happened here...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.81,0:53:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is because of you.
